      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard and preserved in showroom condition. This unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a specimen of unparalleled mechanical and aesthetic integrity. Every surface and component reflects a history of fastidious care, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this benchmark of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
