    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the factory paint\u2019s deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections. The interior is a pristine sanctuary, featuring supple leather upholstery with zero bolster wear and that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed only by certified specialists. With a documented service history and zero mechanical needs, this is a rare opportunity to own an uncompromising example of automotive excellence.",
