      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely flawless! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, it honestly still feels and smells like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home, so I've priced it to move fast. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why I'm so obsessed with it! \u2728",
