      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an immaculate E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8. This specimen boasts an 8,400 RPM redline with razor-sharp throttle response via eight individual throttle bodies. It is equipped with the ZCP Competition Package, including a 10mm lower suspension geometry and specifically tuned Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for enhanced lateral grip. The drivetrain features the tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Preventative maintenance is comprehensive: rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and ARP bolts, and the throttle actuators are upgraded. The chassis remains factory-true with no subframe fatigue. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
